thread.title: Fact sheet: 2016 Scion iM

author: seattlepi.com
title: Fact sheet: 2016 Scion iM
text:
2016 Scion iM
BASE PRICE: $18,460 for iM manual; $19,200 for iM with CVT.
PRICE AS TESTED: $20,334.
TYPE: Front-engine, front-wheel drive, five-passenger, mid-size, five-door hatchback.
ENGINE: 1.8-liter, double overhead cam, four-cylinder with VVT.
MILEAGE: 28 mpg (city), 37 mpg (highway).
TOP SPEED: 110 mph.
LENGTH: 170.5 inches.
WHEELBASE: 102.4 inches.
CURB WEIGHT: 3,031 pounds.
BUILT AT: Japan.
OPTIONS: Carpeted floor mats and cargo mat $185; rear bumper protector $89; wheel locks $65.
DESTINATION CHARGE: $795.
